537201c7496526","tid":2304861,"uid":281117,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-11-20/496967\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-11-20%2F496967&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR1UwqJDRuBhX9JYyxoGH6Hk%3D&h=4cedf3f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-11-20/496967</a><br />\n<br />\n依個傻仔咪係其中之一囉<br />\n2019年去大陸<br />\n間廠2020年已經瀕臨破產、連部光刻機都抵押埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢弘芯去年才高薪挖角大批台積電員工，還延攬前台積電共同營運長蔣尚義擔任執行長，如今因為瀕臨破產、公司營運陷入停擺，連被視為是弘芯招牌的前執行長蔣尚義都對此坦言「根本是場噩夢」。"},{"pid":"e10831c24b578c4829eeb01bcffd64926951abf9","tid":2304861,"uid":147198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T12:56:19.000Z","msg":"唔妥協可以點？<br />\n係大陸拉人 定唔做apple 生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}